{"tid":1144973,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[罕有非膠Post]人與人之間只存在交易，感情只係一場交易","createTime":"2019-05-08T11:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-09T06:08:56.000Z","uid":225098,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b6271e37537e7bbbd6dc4b8254b62c8442b2fe9e","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:37:21.000Z","msg":"所謂嘅感情，只不過係一場交易。<br />\n<br />\n呢一種交易，叫做<strong>慾望交易</strong>。所以「感」就係「慾」。無論係親情、友情定係愛情，都係慾望交易。呢個世界並冇無條件嘅愛，只有建基於得到慾望嘅交易。<br />\n<br />\n父母所謂會「無條件地」養育仔女成人，只係基於滿足自己嘅成就感(養育仔女成人嘅成就)，有甚者只係為咗養兒防老，滿足自己嘅物慾同安全感。<br />\n<br />\n朋友之間如果冇咗互相認同、肯定，朋友嘅關係就並唔存在。所以友情只係基於滿足自己嘅認同感、安全感，有甚者只係為咗得到快樂，滿足自己嘅物慾同權慾。<br />\n<br />\n點解你會愛上佢？佢一定有一啲方面吸引到你同佢交往㗎，所以唔存在純愛情同埋無條件嘅愛情。男女之間只係基於滿足自己嘅認同感、安全感、情慾同性慾，有甚者只係為咗改善生活，滿足自己嘅物慾同權慾。<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273588e5cb7a0f32e33b65419c4780fe7f93c2ab","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"我講過呢個觀點俾社工聽，佢問我洗唔洗咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14683d916464df9e7b9707212f4740959c19a6ca","tid":1144973,"uid":153144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"啱，我愛上你都係一種交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c8ea66873a8b9efdadc2c0360a6455d0767808b","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"14683d916464df9e7b9707212f4740959c19a6ca","tid":1144973,"uid":153144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:39:48.000Z","msg":"啱，我愛上你都係一種交易<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:42:17.000Z","msg":"期待滿足慾望都係一種慾望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"990662dae0010de81a064fa50ba8823200ca6456","tid":1144973,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:49:25.000Z","msg":"不服<br />\n你呢個都係膠post"},{"pid":"802e54897c31862d724d483eccdc6159e1c0f44f","tid":1144973,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273588e5cb7a0f32e33b65419c4780fe7f93c2ab","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"我講過呢個觀點俾社工聽，佢問我洗唔洗咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"唉，個社工都唔show我呀"},{"pid":"bbd731e9a2e4c3d9c672345d7ebf069de6d77d6b","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:54:17.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">簡單合約(Simple contracts)：雖然稱之爲「簡單」，卻不表示它們只涉及毫不複雜的事件，並且容易理解。確切地說，它只是意味著合約的訂立是簡單、容易的。簡單合約是以口頭或不經蓋章的書面形式訂立的合約，它也可以是從行為中推斷出來的。簡單來說，簡單合約的有效性並不取決於特殊的手續。</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n簡單合約係<strong>無形</strong>嘅，亦可以係<strong>無法律效力</strong>嘅。<strong>所有愛情嘅承諾，都屬於簡單合約</strong>，只係慾望交易嘅簡單合約，合約可以隨時無效。"},{"pid":"f465e0ef4a05f3a54741e379e7bbb635d23d5f39","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"802e54897c31862d724d483eccdc6159e1c0f44f","tid":1144973,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273588e5cb7a0f32e33b65419c4780fe7f93c2ab","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"我講過呢個觀點俾社工聽，佢問我洗唔洗咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"唉，個社工都唔show我呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:55:36.000Z","msg":"邊到嘅社工先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb5a7b87e0bea51ebf421c7b059756d32034b5b6","tid":1144973,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"273588e5cb7a0f32e33b65419c4780fe7f93c2ab","tid":1144973,"uid":225098,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-08T11:39:13.000Z","msg":"我講過呢個觀點俾社工聽，佢問我洗唔洗咁灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj